The MYSQL ORDER BY Clause is used to sort the records in ascending or descending order.
syn SELECT expressions  
    FROM tables  
    [WHERE conditions]  
    ORDER BY expression [ ASC | DESC ];
expression - column name that we want to retrieve

we can use order by clause in  SELECT statement,SELECT LIMIT statement, and DELETE LIMIT statement


Mysql order by clause
select * from employee Order By designatiion

Mysql OrderBy clause with ASC/DESC attribute
select * from employee Order By name ASC
select * from employee Order By name DESC